      "Likely bottleneck is partition-specific (mi3001x/mi2104x) rather than uniform across the cluster; could be driven by GPU topology/features/access constraints.",
      "Caveat: saturation metric is CPU-based; to support the workspace’s correlation goal, re-run job-correlation to validate whether mi3001x/mi2104x backlogs align with the thermally hot nodes."
